source: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_Q1_100_000<tab>Y-You want to know what I do? But my name─I thought it was obv─ahem. Very well. What I do is quite simple: I take any of the materials you've collected on the island, and sell them for cowries on your behalf. Don't worry, I <var 1A 02 /var>never<var 1A 01 /var> take anything for myself. Trust me.
target: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_Q1_100_000<tab>Vous pouvez m'échanger les matériaux récupérés sur l'île contre des assignats insulaires et je me chargerai de les exporter<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_SYSTEM_100_000<tab>Sell materials in your isleventory to the enterprising exporter in exchange for islander's cowries.
target: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_SYSTEM_100_000<tab>Les assignats insulaires émeraude s'obtiennent en échangeant vos biens insulaires à Laracheteuse, à la hutte placide.

source: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_SYSTEM_100_005<tab>In addition, the enterprising exporter may be willing to part with seafarer's cowries in exchange for uncommon materials in your isleventory.
target: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_SYSTEM_100_005<tab>Certains matériaux de valeur peuvent lui être échangés contre des assignats insulaires azur.

source: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_Q1_200_000<tab>Why, hello there, friend of the owner! (Pssst, just between you and me, I might have a little something for you...if you've got the cowries.) <bleep> Oh, I didn't see you there, felicitous! Don't you worry, I'm just conversing with this lovely individual here. (Nosy cat bastard...)
target: TEXT_CTSMJIFARMSHOP_00787_Q1_200_000<tab>Bienvenue<var 1D /var>! Je vous souhaite une très bonne visite<var 1D /var>!
